	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2015-08-20T07:39:27">Henderson Opportunities Trust plc is a United Kingdom-based investment trust. The Company's investment objective is to achieve above average capital growth from investment in a portfolio of predominantly United Kingdom companies. The Company's portfolio includes a range of sectors, such as industrials, consumer services, financials, healthcare, technology, basic materials, oil and gas, consumer goods and telecommunications. The Company's investment portfolio includes 4D Pharma, Retroscreen Virology, HSBC, Ricardo, Velocys, Johnson Service, e2v technologies, Royal Dutch Shell B shares, BHP Billiton and Vertu Motors, among others. Henderson Investment Funds Limited is the investment manager of the Company.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2016-02-23T13:22:56">BRIEF: For the fiscal year ended 31 October 2015, Henderson Opportunities Trust plc revenues increased from L3.6M to L11.7M. Net income increased from L2.4M to L9.8M. Revenues reflect Gains from investments held at fair valu increase from L1.9M to L9.3M, Dividends from investments increase of 40% to L2.1M, Dividend income increase of 5% to L214K. Net income benefited from Other administrative expenses decrease of 19% to L128K (expense).</Text>
	</TextInfo>
